{"id":4533,"content":"<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = \"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" /><o:p><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\"></FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 18pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">邓小平的“猫论”问世以来，既得到广大人民群众的认可和拥护，也受到不少人的怀疑和诘难。拥护者认为它用朴素易懂的话说出了关乎改革开放“方法论”的大道理，极大地解放了人们的思想；诘难者认为它给投机取巧的人提供了实用主义的理论武器，让那些些不择手段发财致富人有了可乘之机。“猫论”究竟有没有道理？我想还是从它的原意说起才能讲明白。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 18pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">“猫论”本是邓小平家乡四川的一句俚语：</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 18pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">“不管白猫黑猫，逮住老鼠就是好猫。”（还有一个版本：“不管黄猫黑猫，抓住老鼠就是好猫。”）</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 18pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">我认为，这名俚语说得很有道理，你看：</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 18pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">首先，做事的目的很正确：逮老鼠（消灭四害）；</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 18pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">其次，做事的手段很合理：用猫逮（生态灭鼠）；</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 18pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">再次，做事的效果也很好：逮住老鼠（干出成绩）；</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 18pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">复次，结果的评价很公正：逮住老鼠就是好猫（激励先进）；</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 18pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">最后，手段的差别只在于：猫的皮毛颜色不一样（各具特色）。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 18pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">以上五个方面，谁能找出一个不对的地方呢？我看不好找。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 18pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">我们不妨把这句话作点改变：</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 18pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">不管白猫黑猫，晚上不睡觉就是好猫；</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 18pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">不管白猫黑猫，不偷吃鱼的就是好猫；</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 18pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">不管白猫黑猫，叫得好听的就是好猫；</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 18pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">不管白猫黑猫，能吓跑老鼠就是好猫；</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 18pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">不管瞎猫病猫，逮住老鼠就是好猫；</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 18pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">不管馋猫懒猫，逮住老鼠就是好猫。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 18pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">上面的六句话里，前三句中说的猫虽然都有优点，但是我们不知道它们会不会逮老鼠，所以不能断定它们是好猫；第四句中的猫倒是干点正事，但是效果欠佳，老鼠吓跑了还会再来；后两句中的猫虽然逮住了老鼠，但是有的是“瞎猫逮住死耗子”，有的可能把病传染给主人，有的不守规矩常偷吃，有的十分懒惰肯定逮不住几个老鼠。总而言之，它们都算不上真正的好猫。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 18pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">我们把“不管白猫黑猫，逮住老鼠就是好猫。”这句话和后面修改过的六句话作个比较，就会承认这句俚语中包含着：</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 60pt; TEXT-INDENT: -36pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; tab-stops: list 60.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\"><SPAN style=\"mso-list: Ignore\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">第一，<SPAN style=\"FONT: 7pt Times New Roman\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN></FONT></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">目的的正当性；</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 60pt; TEXT-INDENT: -36pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; tab-stops: list 60.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\"><SPAN style=\"mso-list: Ignore\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">第二，<SPAN style=\"FONT: 7pt Times New Roman\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN></FONT></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">手段的合理性；</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 60pt; TEXT-INDENT: -36pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; tab-stops: list 60.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\"><SPAN style=\"mso-list: Ignore\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">第三，<SPAN style=\"FONT: 7pt Times New Roman\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN></FONT></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">效果的利好性；</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 60pt; TEXT-INDENT: -36pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; tab-stops: list 60.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\"><SPAN style=\"mso-list: Ignore\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">第四，<SPAN style=\"FONT: 7pt Times New Roman\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN></FONT></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">评价的公正性；</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">第五，方法的灵活性。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 18pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">这不正是大家希望看到的改革开放的“正道”吗？</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 18pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">这个“正道”用邓小平的话讲就是“三个有利于”的判断标准，即“是否有利于发展社会主义社会的生产力，是否有利于增强社会主义国家的综合国力，是否有利于提高人民的生活水平。”用这个标准指导改革开放，我们正在建设的社会主义就不会是“大跃进”时代的“叫化子共产主义”，也不会是只问姓“社”姓“资”而不管人民死活的“本本社会主义”，还不会是导致两极分化、不讲共同富裕的权贵资本主义。它是“会逮老鼠的社会主义”，是让中国富强、人民幸福的中国特色社会主义。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\"> <o:p></o:p></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 18pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">至于有些只讲方法的灵活性、不讲目的的正当性的人，他们要么是“馋猫”，要么是“病猫”，要么是“懒猫”。这些人钻改革开放的空子，投机取巧、违法乱纪，为富不仁。他们的所作所为和“猫论”所提倡东西的有着本质的区别，根本够不上“好猫”的条件。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 18pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">如果因为这些人不走“正道”而走“邪路”就把责任推到“猫论”上面，甚至认为“猫论”把改革开放的路子引向了歧途，那么这样的结论显然是不公平的。我看坚持这种结论的人不是糊涂，就是别有用心。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 18pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">一句话：小平的“猫论”没有错，错的是误读和曲解“猫论”的人。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\"><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;<BR><BR></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana\">（该文所表述的内容为作者本人观点，与《炎黄春秋》杂志及炎黄春秋网的观点和立场无关。）</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P></SPAN></FONT></SPAN>","title":"“猫论”错了吗？","time":1235238678999}